- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another likely category as the paper discusses the development and applications of deep neural networks, which are a key component of AI systems.
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is less likely but still possible as the paper may discuss the implementation and optimization of deepESNs.
